data.description: Ranch style home in Carroll School District. You'll find this 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath home just a short walk from Deer Creek Park. This home offers new laminate flooring and some new carpet along with fresh paint. Also, it offers an updated kitchen with stainless appliances as well as updated bathrooms. The roof and windows are less than 10 years old as well as the garage door, heating and air, water heater and water softener.  Enjoy the large back yard which is partially fenced. 2 car attached garage. All on one acre. Move in ready with immediate possession.
